title: ITIL ISIS January 2008 DRB III chrysler software update CD
description:
This is an iso image of the final software update CD that chrysler sent out to the dealers for the DRB III chrysler dealer OBD 2 scanner. It includes all the PCM flash files up through jan 2008 as well. People are trying to sell this one or older versions on ebay for $30-$100. I actually paid $65 for this disc. I am providing it here free of charge so that no one else has to pay for it. 

ITIL ISIS January 2008 DRB III chrysler update CD, final one
